19503600409">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/7619615/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Hepatic+portal+venous+gas%3A+imaging+modalities+and+clinical+significance&amp;author=CG+Schulze&amp;author=U+Blum&amp;author=K+Haag&amp;publication_year=1995&amp;journal=Acta+Radiol&amp;pages=377-380&amp;doi=10.1177%2F028418519503600409&amp;pmid=7619615">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">9.</div><div id="r9" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Marin B, Chouvy V, Denier M, Debard I, Tran-Minh V. Gas in hepatic veins associated with tunneled femoral hemodialysis catheter [in French]. <em>J Radiol</em> 2002;83(1):47–48.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/11965150/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Gas+in+hepatic+veins+associated+with+tunneled+femoral+hemodialysis+catheter+%5Bin+French%5D&amp;author=B+Marin&amp;author=V+Chouvy&amp;author=M+Denier&amp;author=I+Debard&amp;author=V+Tran-Minh&amp;publication_year=2002&amp;journal=J+Radiol&amp;pages=47-48&amp;pmid=11965150">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">10.</div><div id="r10" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Wiesner W, Khurana B, Ji H, Ros PR. CT of acute bowel ischemia. <em>Radiology</em> 2003;226(3):635–650.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1148/radiol.2263011540">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/12601205/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=CT+of+acut